acceptance_criteria: "Given a scanner export (Semgrep CSV, dependabot alert, CodeQL SARIF), when it is imported, then each finding exists as a pm Issue with scanner ID, rule, severity, file#line, platform link, and triage tags, parented under a batch task on pm-qwoy; and pm search by scanner ID or rule finds it without leaving pm."
