body: "# Agent story: security findings as pm context\n\n**As a** maintainer running security scanners over pm-cli,\n**I want** every finding preserved as an individually triageable pm issue (scanner ID as issue code, severity/rule/file tags, platform + code links),\n**so that** any agent can rebuild the full security posture from the pm tracker alone — project management = context management.\n\nExemplar batch: pm-oz8u (Semgrep 2026-07-06, 40 findings). Changelog-excluded per agent-story convention."
